text: Philips Sport Vereniging (English: Philips Sports Union), widely known either as PSV or PSV Eindhoven, is a sports club from Eindhoven, Netherlands. It is best known for its professional football (soccer) section. ==Honours== ===National=== *Eredivisie: 25 ** Winners: 1928–29, 1934–35, 1950–51, 1962–63, 1974–75, 1975–76, 1977–78, 1985–86, 1986–87, 1987–88, 1988–89, 1990–91, 1991–92, 1996–97, 1999–00, 2000–01, 2002–03, 2004–05, 2005–06, 2006–07, 2007–08, 2014–15, 2015–16, 2017–18, 2023/24 *KNVB Cup: 11 ** Winners: 1949–50, 1973–74, 1975–76, 1987–88, 1988–89, 1989–90, 1995–96, 2004–05, 2011–12, 2021/22, 2022/23 *Johan Cruyff Shield: 11 ** Winners: 1992, 1996, 1997, 1998, 2000, 2001, 2003, 2008, 2012, 2015, 2016 (Record) ===International=== *European Cup / UEFA Champions League: 1 ** Winners: 1987–88 *UEFA Cup / UEFA Europa League: 1 ** Winners: 1977–78 ==Current players== ===First-team squad=== ====Players out on loan==== ==League position== ===Former position=== ==References== Category:1910s establishments in the Netherlands Category:1913 establishments in Europe Category:Dutch football clubs Category:Eindhoven
